(837,1,1,'mcq','S2/SS1','Internet and WWW',1,'easy',1,1,'Which device is commonly used to connect to a wireless network?','A laptop can connect to a wireless network using Wi-Fi.',1),
(838,1,1,'mcq','S2/SS1','Internet and WWW',1,'easy',1,1,'What is the function of the back button in a browser?','It returns the user to the previous page.',1),
(839,1,1,'mcq','S2/SS1','Internet and WWW',1,'easy',1,1,'Which internet service allows sending of instant messages?','Instant messaging allows real-time communication.',1),
